<Layout title="Solar Energy Industry">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Solar Energy Industry</h1>
  <p class="mb-4">The solar energy industry is rapidly growing as the world shifts towards renewable energy sources. Solar panels convert sunlight into electricity, providing a clean and sustainable energy solution. The industry encompasses various sectors, including manufacturing, installation, and maintenance of solar panels, as well as research and development of new technologies to improve efficiency and reduce costs.</p>
  <p class="mb-4">Key players in the solar energy industry include companies that produce photovoltaic cells, solar panel manufacturers, and service providers that offer installation and maintenance services. The industry also benefits from government incentives and policies aimed at promoting renewable energy adoption.</p>
  <p class="mb-4">As the demand for clean energy continues to rise, the solar energy industry is expected to see significant growth in the coming years, contributing to a more sustainable future.</p>
</Layout>